snippet.title: Insomnis [PS4/PS5/PC] Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Insomnis is a first-person psychological horror adventure set in a mysterious mansion where strange things will haunt you.

More details here: https://worthplaying.com/game/15798-insomnis/

Insomnis will be available as a PS4 / PS5 exclusive digital-only title on October 29, 2021 for $14.99 / €14,99, while it is also coming to PC (Steam) at some point.
